HEADWORD: Gleed
<hw>Gleed</hw> <pr>(gl⟦emac⟧d)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[AS.
<ets>gl⟦emac⟧d</ets>, fr. <ets>gl⟦omac⟧wan</ets> to glow as a fire; akin
