<ets>gl⟦omac⟧⟦edh⟧</ets>. See <er>Glow</er>, <pos>v. i.</pos>]</ety>
<def>A live or glowing coal; a glede.</def> <mark>[Archaic]</mark>
<rj><au>Chaucer. Longfellow.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
